    Page: 144
    Loc: 1365
By: Li Bai
Format: verse
Title: Sitting
AlternateTitles:
  - Reverence Mountain
---
A flock of birds flies up, then disappears.
One last cloud also drifts into emptiness.

The mountain and I gaze at each other,
untiring, until only the mountain remains.
